title: Transformers RID 2015 S01E09 720p [TankEngine]
description:
Sure, you could have watched it in Chinese, French and Portuguese, but here's Transformers RID 2015 S01E09 in English! This is the first and only place I am uploading it. Please feel free to share it around but remember to give credit where credit is due.

Chapter markings are included for your convenience.

Please note that because of the way this is broadcast, it has been upscaled to 720p and so is not "true" 720p.

Video: 

720p @ 50fps (upscaled from 576i @ 25fps)
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, H.264

Audio:

MPEG-2 Stereo @ 48kHz
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, AAC

Please enjoy this show and make sure to check back next weekend for episodes 10 and 11, with more to come in the future!
